# ============================================================
# IMPORTANT SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================================

# 1. Get a Private Key:
#    Option A - Hardhat local account
#      npx hardhat run --help (creates accounts automatically)
#    
#    Option B - Use existing wallet
#      Export private key from MetaMask/wallet
#      Format: no "0x" prefix, just the 64 hex characters
#
#    Option C - Generate new account
#      node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"

# 2. Fund your account with testnet tokens:
#    NEURO tokens: https://neuroweb.ai/faucet
#    Make sure you have enough for deployment gas + tests

# 3. Optional: Get Subscan API key for contract verification
#    Visit: https://neuroweb-testnet.subscan.io
#    Create account and generate API key

# ============================================================
# DEPLOYMENT WORKFLOW
# ============================================================

# 1. Copy this file:
#    cp .env.example .env

# 2. Edit .env and add your private key:
#    PRIVATE_KEY=your_64_char_hex_string

# 3. Deploy contracts:
#    npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network neuroweb_testnet

# 4. Save the output addresses - you'll need them for frontend

# 5. Optional - verify on Subscan:
#    npx hardhat verify --network neuroweb_testnet CONTRACT_ADDRESS

